::Prowl::

A pained look comes into Prowl's eyes as Iron Raptor snarls at him and walks 
off. He didn't like what he just had to do, but it was nessesary. At least in 
his eyes.

He runs up to her, not sure of what to do. "I'm sorry. I'll never li-" he 
breaks off. That was a promise he probably couldn't keep. He sighs. "You can 
go in robot mode if you want. I can carry you either way."
